The candidate of the Peoples Democratic Party, in Kogi State, Wada Musa has won Yagba West in the November 16th gubernatorial election. Musa scored 8,860 votes against the 7,868 votes recorded by the candidate of the All Progressives Congress, Yahaya Bello.
Yahaya Bello is the incumbent Governor. Wada also won Yagba East Local Government Area. See the result: Yagba West
